geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","content":"这些建议主要面向那些对在现代科技公司担任技术岗位感兴趣的计算机专业大学生，不过，其中很多内容对其他人也同样适用。"},"68":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-15","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","content":"常见的技术岗位有：软件工程师、产品经理、数据科学家、数据工程师或产品设计师等。"},"69":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-16","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#通用建议","content":"**我对学生们的一贯建议可以总结为以下几点：**"},"70":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-17","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#通用建议","content":"探索生命的意义（ikigai），并寻求目标与内心的一致性。"},"71":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-18","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#通用建议","content":"打好心理与身体健康的基础。"},"72":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-19","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#通用建议","content":"开展你热爱的课余项目，并与志同道合的伙伴一起完成。"},"73":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-20","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#通用建议","content":"在职业发展上做出「明智的」投入。"},"74":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-21","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#通用建议","content":"让阅读成为一种习惯，也成为一种热爱。"},"75":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-22","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#通用建议","content":"不要像 NPC 那样随波逐流、缺乏思考！"},"76":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-23","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#通用建议","content":"**关于建议的一点说明**"},"77":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-24","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#通用建议","content":"建议总是依赖于特定语境，也往往是简化的表达，因此并不一定适用于每个人。"},"78":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-25","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#通用建议","content":"接纳那些与你产生共鸣的建议，并时常回顾；无法产生共鸣的也无需强求。"},"79":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-26","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#通用建议","content":"多接触不同的资源，广泛阅读各种想法！"},"80":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-27","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#ikigai存在的意义","content":"人们常用这样一幅维恩图来形象地解释 ikigai（存在的意义）："},"81":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-28","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#ikigai存在的意义","content":"找到你的 ikigai，意味着找到你热爱的事、你擅长的事、这个世界需要的事、以及能为你带来收入的事，这四者的交集。"},"82":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-29","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#ikigai存在的意义","content":"你热爱的事：是那些你在从事时感到真正的乐趣与激情的工作。"},"83":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-30","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#ikigai存在的意义","content":"你能获得报酬的事：是那些能为你带来外在回报，有助于生活与财务的工作。"},"84":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-31","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#ikigai存在的意义","content":"你擅长的事：你的技能与这类工作高度契合，而且你也有持续提升的兴趣。"},"85":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-32","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#ikigai存在的意义","content":"这个世界需要的事：你能为他人创造价值，并感受到自己正在为社会或社群做出贡献。"},"86":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-33","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#ikigai存在的意义","content":"在我与人们探讨职业满足感时，我发现最快乐的人，往往在这四个方面都达到了很高的程度。"},"87":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-34","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#ikigai存在的意义","content":"你也可以从另一个角度思考：寻找那些既能激发你内在热情，又能带来外在回报的机会。\n在职业生涯的早期阶段，你也许更应该关注**成长空间**和**学习潜力**。"},"88":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-35","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#ikigai存在的意义","content":"通常来说，那些兼具内外动机的事情——既让你发自内心地热爱，又带来现实回报——你越有动力去做好，它们成功的可能性也越大。"},"89":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-36","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#ikigai存在的意义","content":"**举几个例子：**"},"90":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-37","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#ikigai存在的意义","content":"我在做一个我热爱的课余项目，它很有意义，同时还能帮助我学习 React。"},"91":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-38","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#ikigai存在的意义","content":"我正在实习，这份工作一方面帮我赚取学费，另一方面让我学到不少新东西。"},"92":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-39","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#ikigai存在的意义","content":"我花时间和我很敬佩的人相处，从他们身上学到很多。"},"93":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-40","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#ikigai存在的意义","content":"我的工作把我热爱的艺术与设计结合在一起，比如在 Figma 这样的公司工作。"},"94":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-41","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#ikigai存在的意义","content":"**理想情况下，几年后你可以达到这样的状态：**"},"95":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-42","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#ikigai存在的意义","content":"我在从事我热爱的工作，和我喜欢的人共事，参与的是与我价值观一致的项目。这份工作既让我不断成长，又能满足我的财务和个人目标。"},"96":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-43","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#ikigai存在的意义","content":"**要实现这样的状态，你可能需要有意识地做出一些努力，比如：**"},"97":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-44","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#ikigai存在的意义","content":"主动进入新环境：寻找朋友、工作、俱乐部或项目；"},"98":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-45","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#ikigai存在的意义","content":"培养良好的环境：建立习惯、主动提问、深化关系；"},"99":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-46","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#ikigai存在的意义","content":"塑造积极的心态：培养感恩、自我记录、持续阅读；"},"100":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-47","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#ikigai存在的意义","content":"为理想工作做好准备：投入于职业成长相关的行动（详见下文）。"},"101":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-48","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#对齐感alignment","content":"在你参与某项活动时，不妨问问自己："},"102":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-49","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#对齐感alignment","content":"我是否真心感到兴奋和投入？"},"103":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-50","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#对齐感alignment","content":"我是否正与那些我敬佩、希望向他们学习的人共处？"},"104":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-51","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#对齐感alignment","content":"这里的氛围是否让我感到自在？是否符合我的价值观？"},"105":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-52","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#对齐感alignment","content":"这条路是否有助于我未来的发展，或者能让我成长？"},"106":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-53","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#对齐感alignment","content":"如果以上问题你都无法肯定回答，那么这很可能是一个「价值观未对齐」的预警信号。"},"107":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-54","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#对齐感alignment","content":"此时你需要认真地反思："},"108":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-55","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#对齐感alignment","content":"> 我做这件事，是因为我真心想做，还是因为别人告诉我应该做？"},"109":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-56","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#对齐感alignment","content":"> 我是因为觉得这条路是默认的选项、难以改变，才走上这条路的吗？"},"110":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-57","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#对齐感alignment","content":"随着时间推移，你会逐渐建立起一种更敏锐的「感知雷达」，帮助你判断哪些事情与你对齐、哪些没有。\n这种直觉将引导你走向更契合自我、更幸福、更充实的生活。🙂"},"111":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-58","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#打好身心健康的基础","content":"这意味着："},"112":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-59","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#打好身心健康的基础","content":"均衡饮食 🙂"},"113":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-60","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#打好身心健康的基础","content":"保证充足的锻炼和睡眠"},"114":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-61","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#打好身心健康的基础","content":"接受心理治疗、按时就医、合理使用药物"},"115":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-62","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#打好身心健康的基础","content":"发展能带来快乐和意义的兴趣和朋友"},"116":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-63","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#打好身心健康的基础","content":"向身边的人寻求帮助和建议！"},"117":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-64","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#打好身心健康的基础","content":"当然，也可能意味着你需要做出一些权衡，比如："},"118":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-65","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#打好身心健康的基础","content":"明确划分工作、学习与生活的界限，保持心理平衡"},"119":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-66","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#打好身心健康的基础","content":"减少与不能带来快乐的人或活动的接触时间"},"120":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-67","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#打好身心健康的基础","content":"通过申请额外的学生贷款来负担更好的膳食计划"},"121":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-68","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#打好身心健康的基础","content":"饮食更健康、减少社交应酬和饮酒频率"},"122":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-69","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#打好身心健康的基础","content":"没有坚实的身心健康基础，其它一切都难以顺利展开。"},"123":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-70","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#打好身心健康的基础","content":"我个人非常喜欢使用 Daylio 作为每日日志工具，用来记录情绪、健康和习惯。当状态不太好时，往往就是它提醒我该调整了。iOS 上的 Sleep Cycle 睡眠 app 也很推荐！"},"124":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-71","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#打好身心健康的基础","content":"这听起来也许是显而易见的道理，但我认为多数人对健康的投入都远远不够，往往等到真的生病了才开始重视。"},"125":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-72","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#打好身心健康的基础","content":"锻炼、睡眠和饮食能带来巨大变化（比如快乐 +30%，精力 +50%，成果也 +50%），但却总被我们忽略。"},"126":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-73","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#打好身心健康的基础","content":"顺便说一句，非常推荐 Huberman 的播客，值得一听。🙂"},"127":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-74","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#开展你热爱的课余项目","content":"做课余项目通常很有价值，它们可以："},"128":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-75","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#开展你热爱的课余项目","content":"向雇主展示你的经验、兴趣和价值观"},"129":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-76","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students#开展你热爱的课余项目","content":"帮你探索新主题、新想法"},"130":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students-77","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/advice-for-students",