k-lab/learn-databse","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/learn-databse#数据库","content":"数据库（Database，DB）是**存储在计算机内、有组织的、可共享的**相关数据的集合，这种集合按一定的数据模型组织、描述并长期存储，同时能够以安全可靠的方法对数据进行检索。"},"334":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/learn-databse-8","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/learn-databse","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/learn-databse#数据库系统","content":"数据库系统（Database System，DBS）是指在计算机系统中引入数据库后的系统。&#x2A;*它主要由数据库、数据库用户、计算机硬件系统和计算机软件系统（含数据库管理系统）等几部分组成。**"},"335":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/learn-databse-9","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/learn-databse","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/learn-databse#数据库管理系统","content":"数据库管理系统（Database Management System，DBMS）是指建立、运用、管理和维护数据库，并对数据库进行统一控制的系统软件。"},"336":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/learn-databse-10","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/learn-databse","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/learn-databse#数据库管理系统","content":"常见的数据库管理系统有 SQL Server、Oracle、MySQL、Access等。"},"337":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/learn-databse-11","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/learn-databse","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/learn-databse#结论","content":"Data \\< DB \\< DBMS \\< DBS"},"338":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/learn-databse-12","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/learn-databse","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/learn-databse#结论","content":"*注意：DBMS 是 DBS 的必要组成部分，没有 DBMS 的 DBS 在实际中是不存在的。*"},"339":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"page","content":"使用 Fumadocs 搭建博客","breadcrumbs":["Docs","折腾笔记"],"tags":[],"url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs"},"340":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-0","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","tags":[],"type":"text","url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","content":"Making a Blog with Fumadocs 的译文"},"341":{"id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs-1","page_id":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blog-with-fumadocs","type":"heading","tags":[],"url":"/notes/geek-lab/making-a-blo